<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Alegreya+SC:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,400;1,500;1,700;1,800;1,900&family=Archivo:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&family=Delius&family=Nunito:ital,wght@0,200..1000;1,200..1000&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">  
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Alegreya+SC:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,400;1,500;1,700;1,800;1,900&family=Archivo:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&family=Delius&family=Nunito:ital,wght@0,200..1000;1,200..1000&family=Roboto+Serif:ital,opsz,wght@0,8..144,100..900;1,8..144,100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/uv.css">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Current UV Index In <%= cityName %> is:  <span class="index"><%= uv %></span></h1>
        <h2 class="uvMax">Strongest UV index for today is <span class="max-index"><%= uvMax %></span> at <%= maxUvTime %></h2>

        <% if (uv <= 2) { %>
            <div class="safe-tip">
                <h2 class="advice">For current UV index:<br />You can safely enjoy being outside!</h2>
                <p class="tip-detail">Even for very sensitive fair-skinned people, the risk of short-term and long-term UV damage below a UVI of 2 is limited, <br />and under normal circumstances no protective measures are needed.</p>
            </div>
        <% } else if (uv >=3 && uv <=7) { %>
            <div class="tip">
                <h2 class="advice">For current UV index:<br /> We recommend to seek shade during <span class="strong">midday hours!</span> <br />Slip on a <span class="strong">shirt,</span> slop on <span class="strong">sunscreen</span> and slap on <span class="strong">hat!</span></h2>
                <p class="advice-detail"> If sun protection is required, this should include all protective means, i.e. clothing, hat and sunglasses, shade and sunscreen.</p>
            </div>
            <% } else { %> 
            <div class="tip">
                <h2 class="advice">For current UV index:<br /> We recommend to avoid being outside during <span class="strong">midday hours!</span> <br />Make sure you seek shade! <span class="strong">Shirt, sunscreen and hat</span> are a must!</h2>
                <p class="advice-detail"> If sun protection is required, this should include all protective means, i.e. clothing, hat and sunglasses, shade and sunscreen.</p>
            </div>
            <% } %>
            

        <div class="button">
            <a href="/"><button>Go back to home page</button></a>
        </div>
 
    </div>  
    
    <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>
</body>
</html>